show.description: Lilith was set to lead the Silver Claw pack, but her sister Serena betrayed her, killing their parents and framing Lilith to steal the Alpha title. Branded a rogue, Lilith finds safety—and love—with Tristan, the kind Alpha of the Starlight pack. Together, they uncover Serena’s lies, bring her down, and unite their packs.
